sep.gaia.resources.poi

Class PointOfInterest

  • java.lang.Object
    • sep.gaia.resources.DataResource
      • sep.gaia.resources.poi.PointOfInterest
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MarkerResource, WikipediaData

    public class PointOfInterest
extends DataResource
    Represents a geographical point with certain attributes that might be of interest for a user. Points of Interest (POI) can be ordered in categories and subcategories. The attributes are stored as mapped key-value pairs in textual representation.
    Author:
    Matthias Fisch (Implementation Fabian Buske, Max Witzelsperger)
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
